description: This common Parvati purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 108, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 3 for East, Stringalong for South, and Box for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [108 Votes, Common]
